%^BOLD%^-=%^BLACK%^Repose Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Concerned with the realm of the dead, the repose domain allows the caster to access certain powers from the Limbo.  The domain does not in any way use souls trapped here.

Clerics with the Repose Domain gain the following benefits:
- Immunity to death effects.

The repose domain contains the following spells:

Speak with Dead, Gentle Repose, Undeath is Death, Waves of Exhaustion, Wail of The Banshee

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lysara

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
